== Why a Robotic Arm?

A robotic arm is one of the most commonly used types of robots in the real world.

It is an excellent model for learning because:
- It is simple to understand step by step  
- It clearly shows how joints and movement work  
- It connects directly to real engineering systems  

Unlike wheeled robots or flying drones, a robotic arm focuses on precise and controlled movement, similar to how a human hand works.

