== What You Will Learn from This Model

By studying and building a robotic arm model, you will work with:

- 3D-printed mechanical structures  
- Servo motors for controlled movement  
- Motor driver circuits  
- Microcontrollers such as Arduino Nano  
- Basic wiring and control systems  

You will learn how these parts work together to create controlled motion.

