== Learning Outcomes

By the end of this learning experience, you will be able to:
- Understand how mechanical systems are assembled  
- Learn basic electronics and connections  
- Understand simple programming concepts  
- Explore how robotic systems are designed  
- Develop problem-solving and engineering thinking skills  

Most importantly, you will begin to understand how real-world machines are designed and built.